# Compiled Go binaries (go build / go install artifacts). A `go build` in
# scripts/e2e_vision/ produces scripts/e2e_vision/e2e_vision (named after the
# dir). `go build ./scripts/menuscan` writes ./menuscan to the CWD. The root
# `go build .` produces ./fodmap. Ignore all these shapes.
